This paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus is on multiple agents interacting with each other, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also discusses resource limitations and communication constraints, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
